Avoidable Mortality Attributable to Anthropogenic Fine Particulate Matter 
(PM(2.5)) in Australia.

Hanigan IC(1)(2)(3), Broome RA(3)(4), Chaston TB(1), Cope M(3)(5), Dennekamp 
M(3)(6)(7), Heyworth JS(3)(8), Heathcote K(1)(9), Horsley JA(1), Jalaludin 
